* Follow UDF\nBest Practices
** DO
***_ Keep logic simple (CASE, boolean)
***_ Stay deterministic
***_ Reference only table columns
***_ Test at scale (1M+ rows)
** AVOID
***_ is_account_group_member() in UDF
***_ Complex subqueries / joins
***_ Heavy regex on large text
***_ Non-deterministic logic
** Separation of concerns
***_ Policy: WHO the rules apply to
***_ UDF: HOW to transform the data
** Performance impact
***_ Runs on every query
***_ Enables predicate pushdown
***_ Allows query optimization
@endmindmap
